_From [karthikt...@gmail.com](https://code.google.com/u/118033818539569850455/) on July 26, 2010 19:26:36_

What steps will reproduce the problem? Vector3.java

line 478:

```
public float dot(int x, int y, int z) { 
    return this.x * x + this.y * y + this.z * z;
}
```

it should be:
    public float dot(float x, float y, float z) { 
        return this.x \* x + this.y \* y + this.z \* z;
    }

no reason to take only int arguments

